{"tid":1477614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"814深水埗黑警瞄準記者同市民射催淚彈<有片>","createTime":"2019-08-16T07:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T18:14:53.000Z","uid":90349,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"813c0a6fd81054f908df9deb8960500eb1a9d79b","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:37:28.000Z","msg":"朋友借ac代po 開緊live嘅時候錄影:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/353973423?ref=em-share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F353973423%3Fref%3Dem-share&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=e19ebea0\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/353973423?ref=em-share</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n呢段係本人尋晚嘅所見所聞 <br />\n見證啲狗專瞄路人或記者打<br />\n以及見證街道係冇示威者情況下依舊照嚟個催淚放題<br />\n現場當時橋中間只有我同一位記者<br />\n我當時冇任何防裝 <br />\n而且大部分人係橋嘅左右兩旁<br />\n你細心睇會見到催淚彈嘅軌道係直飛上橋再中欄杆<br />\n同埋會見到黑轉橙旗時前面都係冇人<br />\n當時大部分人已經退到長沙灣道打後<br />\n究竟點解仲要繼續放催淚彈呢？<br />\n<br />\n睇返8月15日狗嘅記招<br />\n深水埗指揮官指出：<br />\n當時遇上暴徒攻擊又彈珠鐵通咁<br />\n唯有使用最低武力 &mdash; 催淚彈<br />\n但其實現場只係和平燒衣<br />\n各大直播亦見唔到任何暴力事件<br />\n當日狗招根本係指黑為白<br />\n再加上有post講狗放題嘅陰謀論<br />\n所以post呢段片，以正視聽！<br />\n<br />\n現場全部都係記者同路人 <br />\n所以唔打格仔啦<br />\n完全冇人有口罩或頭盔<br />\n睇返射催淚彈嘅角度<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n根本就係謀殺</span>"},{"pid":"4ddb4d52968c8d9dafedf5f713d1d041d75e7f7a","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"4c8692c78afdf2b0ec8ccfe30b916e3eb53cfa27","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"710b670001405be2c4eb43d151ff3dcb28545a7c","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ebae7e10a403399240d4b3d0a831f5fe5ee9758a","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"7cc49a375a68aaa86233e9c5a3f79c6b78b3a32b","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"039fdb5300f529e6d0333cc94f2190641cc13af7","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"a1e68735beba7797293ec6884ebfff74cbbce0f7","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:39:17.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"ae1d3d807b2905779c29f7e00a14d1fa80071673","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"c572e08f525e13060cb83223e5b2f4a02d3408eb","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"7ab8c485142fd200fc64427c4c3c07cb26277af4","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"18c09c5873f3534d4c703abdde317b58b2b0a78b","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"35df2a9b30e4595e878a8b1481965284c54d80d5","tid":1477614,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baa0cf07e6393bdc50705b8b20218e91daba44ba","tid":1477614,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbba284033f6502ea2273007f1f97ab1fbbf3a39","tid":1477614,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b692abe741f0495a785a29c4c429fcecb82929c2","tid":1477614,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:42:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲<br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, 999唔通<br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 太古站開槍 意圖製造人踩人<br />\n6. 製造偽証<br />\n7.執行私刑 毆打被捕市民"},{"pid":"4367b42ef96f7b10f0b1f609b7e04000eca754bb","tid":1477614,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"恐怖襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152515de90ef5afbf83609874a8d2238cb946e27","tid":1477614,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:44:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f4f5f82f9e729eb5427d6560bd7a9b0676735fe","tid":1477614,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:45:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a75090deae3ab124386073ddcb85bf92f634fc9","tid":1477614,"uid":82452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0945e857d584d2a832b6382cf88eacc871f2eb94","tid":1477614,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f5f5112b9582fd066a265c433dc29903a15a35","tid":1477614,"uid":296084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"成粒彈影到勁清咁飛過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者哥哥你有冇事?"},{"pid":"34af15864dc8fb60645539efefa949b0fd77d41c","tid":1477614,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703ecea7c976d5f3ce057da4f4f23c5018a101d9","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"62f5f5112b9582fd066a265c433dc29903a15a35","tid":1477614,"uid":296084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"成粒彈影到勁清咁飛過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者哥哥你有冇事?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:14:02.000Z","msg":"佢無事 粒彈中咗柱<br />\n利:我個fd係路過 非記者"},{"pid":"224504863aadcda9f4e40536d32edde12cb056ab","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:14:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8742f88c7193934397e9af32ff940e34e7b7fe0","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3524fe2f6ab520b09e63c805622a52586a40851","tid":1477614,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:18:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚8點遮打見 <br />\n817紅磡見 <br />\n818維園見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f7b23f70aeedce263f145de47cbfb7d9aacfa92e","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:37:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e60d5bb66e468f53c8a4330c16a32ac6c1109bb4","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57b363bda9fe1454eb503cbbff76c6a08b4f0a6a","tid":1477614,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"推到漫山遍野連儂牆818五大訴求文宣（追究721 85 811），重申七一宣言，定立死線<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#解散警隊<br />\n#永遠抵制元朗荃灣北角所有商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"75d2792d4e90f1426dff03d1896f6510d7f4d270","tid":1477614,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8dcba1f4c566901d9dfcac898a3e4e00a6d8061","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2089c42df9877c2cdf8748b1c7210d25f0fe235a","tid":1477614,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a387977293702f2268d1bc9307b00bfa5c3f03a4","tid":1477614,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"對方策略黎"},{"pid":"0a4300e4904335a2913f0c05f7977a991484f32e","tid":1477614,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f6ec41b6c7da22261f49d0c9ba58ff8e9a45971","tid":1477614,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"其實嗰日仲有一單企圖謀殺長者街坊，<br />\n一開波時有粒催淚彈特登射去警署對面後巷，<br />\n條後巷剩係得食花生既街坊，個個都係銀髮長者，仲要粒催淚彈係長者頭頂飛過落喺後巷中間，搞到班長者都冇得離開硬食催淚神經毒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf408368a145ad904a8d4e0430944f59ba53d576","tid":1477614,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:15:41.000Z","msg":"因果由國, 容港治己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hk